3T07:18:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我屌....好在有個老竇係度<br />\n<br />\n唔係就重現死神來了個SHOT...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n垃圾保養公司，今次比佢過到骨，無搞出人命"},{"pid":"f5a678dc9e2f99268020d5df7297e6dd51cc94c6","tid":167477,"uid":15883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T07:26:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>其士執升降機真係垃撚圾！我屋企大廈都係其士做，執完都係一堆問題，點執都執唔好</strong></span></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n升降機機齡舊都係其中一個原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：住緊座樓一直都係用緊呢間<br />\n部𨋢以前個個星期都壞幾次，翻新左之後好少見到壞𨋢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9b460de2c047eb93ea571e1c0e7c7de94c367e4","tid":167477,"uid":15883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T07:32:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20020102/2353291\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20020102%2F2353291&d=r5q0VKZH5TKX5M4XK8oFTcP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=3c2af4de\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20020102%2F2353291&h=6a7312a0\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20020102/2353291</a><br />\n<br />\n差啲就重演15年前嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"328b60ba3c76947339fa097afdf17743d92e27fc","tid":167477,"uid":51796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T07:36:00.000Z","msg":"老豆好波"},{"pid":"2f039f1ba1ef43b8cd04ab51d5a7a5201032af27","tid":167477,"uid":92,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T07:37:28.000Z","msg":"有陰影 唔敢再搭lift"},{"pid":"263502d77c090420dfa1ca0e8fc6be230a181dbd","tid":167477,"uid":4179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T07:45:15.0